rld%2F20191210%2Fsweden-ambassador-china%2Fzh-hant%2F&d=2snho0MtSZbn8sjHWbtmpW5pKsuoI6OgBDFn4N8w%2Bso%3D&h=e8f905b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cn.nytimes.com/world/20191210/sweden-ambassador-china/zh-hant/</a><br />\n<br />\n瑞典前駐華大使被控「與外國勢力談判時恣意妄為」，此前她與兩名代表中國國家利益的人士進行了瑞典檢察官週一所說的未經授權的會面。<br />\n<br />\n這項指控是四年前一起案件的最新轉折，該案中一名瑞典公民被人從泰國祕密帶到中國，瑞典大使在斯德哥爾摩一家酒店舉行當局所謂的祕密會面，中瑞關係從此緊張。<br />\n<br />\n前大使林戴安(Anna Lindstedt)今年早些時候被指控在一月安排安吉拉&middot;桂(Angela Gui)與兩名中國男子會談，他們願意提供幫助釋放她父親&mdash;&mdash;在中國被拘留的瑞典書商桂民海。然而他們並沒有談論釋放她父親的事情，安吉拉&middot;桂說，反而被施壓要求保持沉默。瑞典前駐華大使被控「與外國勢力談判時恣意妄為」，此前她與兩名代表中國國家利益的人士進行了瑞典檢察官週一所說的未經授權的會面。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4618b7a754969b0e65a5c6bae97617a155e76bf5","tid":1896179,"uid":63846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T04:23:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MUtGcCm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMUtGcCm.jpg&h=f946342c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n被中国人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40f15e884ea21442e41cd7820e3ad4296845256e","tid":1896179,"uid":39872,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T04:27:59.000Z","msg":"得喇得喇，国際制裁中共官員唔須要報道，只須要共匪官即時失去世界自由及財富凍結"},{"pid":"e263c0cf18269f9fb592e9347afab3638a659bab","tid":1896179,"uid":229492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T04:39:03.000Z","msg":"痴撚線 推"},{"pid":"36f37c0c82136efcda042afa3439337adf7bc5a5","tid":1896179,"uid":229492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T04:51:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fa3cf2e81284d338e53144f695a3be9fb28d82b5","tid":1896179,"uid":288304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38bb7e85b64a746c3b58cf